org.apache.polygene.api.association

Class NamedAssociationWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.polygene.api.association.NamedAssociationWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<String>, AbstractAssociation, NamedAssociation<Object>

    public class NamedAssociationWrapper
extends Object
implements NamedAssociation<Object>
    If you want to catch calls to NamedAssociations, then create a GenericConcern that wraps the Polygene-supplied NamedAssociations instance with NamedAssociationsWrapper. Override methods to perform your custom code.
